---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

import Card from '../../layouts/Card.astro';
---
<Card title="Monitoring" metaDescription="With monitoring you can outsource the accessibility of your service.">
  <section class="text-center space-y-4">
    <h1>Monitoring</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-left">Monitoring service <strong>frees</strong> you to focus on other things. Allow me to help you take care of improvements.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-left">Monitoring is done with a tool of your choosing. If you already use a monitoring tool such as Webwarden or Siteimprove, you don't need to get an extra tool. Just provide me access and I can help you get more out of your tool.</p>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="services-title">
    <span id="services-title" class="sr-only">The services I offer</span>
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <article class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume flex items-center">Light</h2>
          <p><em class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Monitoring for a less frequently updated service</em></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Monitoring of the automated tool</li>
              <li>Revisions to content as agreed</li>
              <li>Monthly report</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Price: 300 € + VAT per month</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume flex items-center">Comprehensive</h2>
          <p><em class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Monitoring for a regularly updated service</em></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Monitoring of the automated tool</li>
              <li>Light manual testing</li>
              <li>Revisions to content as agreed</li>
              <li>Monthly report</li>
              <li>Awareness session two times a year</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Price: 500 € + VAT per month</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume flex items-center">Extensive</h2>
          <p><em class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">For a service for which accessibility is more than just minimum requirements</em></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 list-disc list-outside pl-3">
              <li>Monitoring of the automated tool</li>
              <li>Manual testing</li>
              <li>Revisions to content as agreed</li>
              <li>Monthly report</li>
              <li>Awareness session four times a year</li>
              <li>Co-ideation of expert and client and adoption of practices (2h / month)</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Price: 900 € + VAT per month</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20 flex flex-col justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume flex items-center">Fully tailored</h2>
          <p><em class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">For a service with specific needs</em></p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            If none of the predefined packages fit your needs, we can create a fully tailored monitoring plan together.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            The tailored plan can include, for example, more frequent manual testing, specific focus areas, or additional training sessions for your team.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Or if your service is smaller, the plan can include less time or, for example, a bi-monthly cycle.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Pricing depends on your needs</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="me" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20">
    <h2 id="content" class="font-bold text-xl text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume">Service level benefits</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3 mt-4">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 ">
        <Icon name="shield-check" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>
          <h3>Benefits of monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Continuous monitoring speeds up the identification of accessibility problems.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">Problems are not allowed to accumulate between accessibility audits.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">Even a less frequently updated website needs accessibility care.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 ">
        <Icon name="book-open" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>
          <h3>Awareness sessions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">During monitoring, we always can identify recurring challenges.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">In a 30-minute awareness sessions for content creators, we will go through recurring challenges and how to improve them.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 ">
        <Icon name="rocket-launch" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>          
          <h3>Co-ideation sessions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Accessibility regulations only set minimum requirements for accessibility</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">The extensive package also includes expert brainstorming to take accessibility beyond the requirements, towards what we call "true accessibility". Ideas are discussed together and refined into suitable development measures.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">Ideation can be done from both usability and accessibility perspectives. I actively follow the discussions and the development of requirements both in Finland and internationally.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section aria-labelledby="me" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-white/50 bg-white/95 dark:bg-black/40 dark:border-black/20">
    <h2 id="options" class="font-bold text-xl text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume">What you get with the monitoring service</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3 mt-4">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 ">
        <Icon name="document" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>
          <h3>Monthly report</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              We can decide together the content of the monthly report. Typically, it includes an overview of identified issues, their severity, and recommendations for improvement.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
              If I have access to the service, the report will also include the actions taken to resolve issues.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 ">
        <Icon name="pencil" class="h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>
          <h3>Issue remediation</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              I can help you fix content issues without you having to do anything. All I need is access to your content management system.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
              I can also help with technical/visual issues if I have access to the code repository or development environment. I can also support your team with the fixes, if we agree on it.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
              NB! The remediation of issues is always done within the agreed monitoring hours.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 ">
        <Icon name="calendar" class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-dk-purple-header dark:text-lt-perfume" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div>
          <h3>Package changes</h3>
          <div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              The level of the package you choose may be subject to change with one month's notice.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mt-6">
              We can decide together the duration of the monitoring service. Typical monitoring contracts are continuous, but we can define a fixed-term contract if needed.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="text-center space-y-4">
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Interested in working together?</p>
    <a href="mailto:sanna@a11y.ing" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-dk-purple-header dark:bg-lt-perfume text-white dark:text-black font-medium hover:opacity-90">Contact me</a>
  </section>
</Card>